Usage: specifyScanChain [-help] <scanChainName>
                        -start { <ftname> | <instPinName> }
                        -stop { <ftname> | <instPinName> }

-help                                   # Prints out the command usage
<scanChainName>                         # name of scan chain (string, required)
-start { <ftname> | <instPinName> }     # name of scan chain start point
                                        # (string, required)
-stop { <ftname> | <instPinName> }      # name of scan chain stop point
                                        # (string, required)